name: Pyth Network
reason: The Oracle Monopoly. Massive locked supply awaiting release. Token is purely a tax on data consumption.

name: Wormhole
reason: The Bridge Troll. 82% of supply locked at launch. Represents the ultimate 'VC Exit Liquidity' vehicle.

name: Jito
reason: Bureaucratic Governance. The protocol (JitoSOL) is great; the token (JTO) is a useless governance coupon with high inflation.

name: Neon EVM
reason: Ethereum emulation on Solana. Heavy VC allocation. Utility is abstract compared to native production.

name: Zeus Network
reason: Bitcoin-Solana communication layer. Lower VC overhang than Wormhole. Enables hard money inflow.

name: deBridge
reason: Cross-chain liquidity layer. Another 'Points Program' token launch that favors farmers over builders.

name: Picasso
reason: Bringing IBC (Cosmos) to Solana. Technical merit is high; token distribution is fairer than W/PYTH.

name: Lumerin
reason: Hashrate routing marketplace. Technically DePIN but functions as infrastructure routing.
